OnAction (GUI item event)
=========================

On most item types, called when the user clicks on a [GUI item](GUI\_items) with the mouse.

On [editDefs](EditDef\_(GUI\_item\_type)), this is called when the text changes.

On [choiceDefs](ChoiceDef\_(GUI\_item\_type)), this is called when the selected option changes.

